  <brief_title>Myocardial Salvage Assessed by Cardiovascular Magnetic Resonance - Impact on Outcome</brief_title>
  <official_title>Prognostic Significance and Determinants of Myocardial Salvage Assessed by Cardiovascular Magnetic Resonance in Acute Reperfused Myocardial Infarction</official_title>
  <sponsors>
